      "_id": "dfYOVUSvrD8ynsBh",
      "name": "Scale Dust",
      "type": "feat",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p> The scarab releases magical glittering dust from its wings. Each creature within 5 feet of the scarab must succeed on a [[/save dex 13 format=long]] or be outlined in blue light for 10 minutes. While outlined in this way, a creature sheds dim light in a 10-foot radius and can’t benefit from being &amp;Reference[invisible]{invisible}. In addition, every &amp;Reference[dragon]{Dragon} within 1 mile of the creature becomes aware of it and can unerringly track the creature. Casting dispel magic on the creature ends the effect on it.</p>\n</section>\nThe [[lookup @name]] uses [[lookup @item.name]] and a save is required.\n</div>",
          "chat": ""
        },
